query:
SELECT s.id, s.companyName, sr.serviceType, sr.serviceLevel, sr.rateUsdCents, sr.countryCode, sr.cityId
FROM suppliers s 
JOIN supplierCoverageCountries scc ON s.id = scc.supplierId 
LEFT JOIN supplierRates sr ON s.id = sr.supplierId AND sr.countryCode = 'AU'
WHERE scc.countryCode = 'AU' AND sr.serviceType = 'L1_NETWORK';
